  <part xml:id="console.ui.manual">
    <title>Administration Console</title>
    <partintro>
      <para> This part gives an introduction to the OpenEngSB Console . It shows the functionality
        and gives an idea what the admin can change in the system and how this is done in the
        console. </para>
      <para>The target audience of this part are users and in special admins of the system.</para>
    </partintro>
